    think='Now I have a comprehensive understanding of the codebase. Let me comp
ile my findings.\n\nThis PR (`feat/issue-1`, PR #6) appears to be implementing t
he infrastructure bootstrap task (`TASK-infrastructure-bootstrap.md`) plus some 
