mplete. The `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/` directory doesn\'t exist at all. No 
Auth BLoC, no login page, no secure storage, no Dio interceptor.\n- ❌ The Auth 
module in API is just a skeleton/stub - `AuthService.register()` returns a stub 
user ID without creating a DB record, `login()` returns stub tokens without any 
real JWT or SMS validation.\n- ❌ Missing JWT Guard (`apps/api/src/common/guards
/jwt-auth.guard.ts` referenced in docs but doesn\'t exist).\n- ❌ Missing `GET /
auth/me`, `POST /auth/refresh`, `POST /auth/logout` endpoints (only `register` a
nd `login` exist, and they\'re stubs).\n- ❌ The API contract (`auth.yaml`) defi
nes `POST /auth/login` with `phone` and `sms_code`, but the controller has a sep
arate `POST /auth/register` endpoint with `birth_date` that doesn\'t match the c
ontract.\n\n### 2. 规范符合性 (Spec compliance)\n- ❌ `RegisterDto` has NO `clas
s-validator` decorators, violating `docs/design-docs/nestjs.md` which requires a
ll input DTOs to use `class-validator` + `class-transformer`.\n- ❌ The auth con
troller route is `api/v1/auth` but `main.ts` already sets global prefix `api/v1`
, so routes become `/api/v1/api/v1/auth/register` - that\'s a bug.\n- ❌ The blo
cks controller route is `/blocks` without the global prefix - actually with glob
al prefix it becomes `/api/v1/blocks`, but the other controllers also don\'t hav
e the prefix... Wait, looking at the controllers:\n  - `AuthController`: `@Contr
oller("api/v1/auth")` - this would result in `/api/v1/api/v1/auth` because of gl
obal prefix\n  - `BlocksController`: `@Controller("blocks")` - results in `/api/
v1/blocks`\n  - `ReportsController`: `@Controller("reports")` - results in `/api
/v1/reports`\n  - `ContentModerationController`: `@Controller("webhooks/moderati
on")` - results in `/api/v1/webhooks/moderation`\n  - `AdminController`: `@Contr
oller("admin/users")` - results in `/api/v1/admin/users`\n  - `HealthController`
: `@Controller("health")` - results in `/api/v1/health`\n\n  So AuthController h
as a BUG - double `/api/v1` prefix.\n\n- ❌ Missing module docs: `docs/modules/a
dmin.md`, `docs/modules/blocks-reports.md`, `docs/modules/content-moderation.md`
are referenced in `docs/modules/INDEX.md` but don\'t exist.\n\n### 3. 契约一致性
(Contract consistency)\n- ❌ The `auth.yaml` defines `POST /api/v1/auth/login` w
ith `phone` and `sms_code`, but the actual controller has:\n  - `POST /api/v1/ap
i/v1/auth/register` with `phone` and `birth_date` (doesn\'t match YAML)\n  - `PO
ST /api/v1/api/v1/auth/login` with no body (doesn\'t match YAML)\n- ❌ `Register
Dto` uses `birth_date` but the OpenAPI contract doesn\'t define this field in `L
oginRequest`.\n- ❌ The generated models in `packages/shared-types/` and `apps/m
obile/lib/models/generated/` match the YAML, but the actual API implementation d
oesn\'t match either the YAML or the generated models.\n\n### 4. 测试覆盖 (Test 
coverage)\n- ❌ BDD step definitions are all empty stubs (`common.js` has empty 
function bodies for all steps).\n- ⚠️ Only `auth.service.spec.ts` and `age-calcul
ator.spec.ts` have real tests. Other modules have no tests.\n- ⚠️ The BDD tests u
se `.steps.js` files with `autoBindSteps` but the step implementations are all n
o-ops.\n\n### 5. 文档同步 (Documentation sync)\n- ❌ `docs/modules/INDEX.md` ref
erences `admin.md`, `blocks-reports.md`, `content-moderation.md` which don\'t ex
ist.\n- ❌ `docs/modules/auth.md` references `apps/api/src/common/guards/jwt-aut
h.guard.ts` and Flutter auth BLoC that don\'t exist.\n- ❌ `docs/QUALITY_SCORE.m
d` says Auth/Matching/IM/Profile/Design System are "❌ 未开始" (not started) but
this PR has actually added significant code. It needs updating.\n\n### 6. 可运行
性 (Runnability)\n- ❌ `make check-docs` would fail because of missing required 
docs (`docs/QUALITY_SCORE.md` exists but the dead link checker might find issues
