check-docs` directly unless they\'re linked from somewhere. But `docs/modules/IN
DEX.md` links to them, so the dead link checker WOULD catch them!)\n- ❌ `make l
int` might fail because of the `@Controller("api/v1/auth")` issue and other code
quality issues.\n- ❌ `make test` - the BDD tests with empty stubs might pass (s
ince they don\'t assert anything), but they\'re not real tests.\n\nLet me verify
